---
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <title>About AirTalk - Anonymous Voice & Text Chat Platform</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Learn about AirTalk, the platform for anonymous voice and text conversations with strangers worldwide." />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/global.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Navbar />
    
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="page-title">About AirTalk</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">
          Dream of finding new friends? Need someone to talk to? Do you want to share your highs and lows?
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-intro">
          <div class="about-illustration">üë•</div>
          <div class="about-text">
            <p>
              AirTalk is an upcoming random voice talk website that provides the best means of talking with strangers. 
              It is an online platform where you can exchange ideas, pick up knowledge from others, and forge deep connections. 
              This is a great way to meet new friends or find someone online to chat with on a live call. It's an exciting, fun, 
              and FREE new way to connect.
            </p>
            <p>
              You can share your likes, build friendship with people you find interesting, or discover people with similar 
              interests just to talk. Join thousands of people every day to connect and spark meaningful conversations with 
              strangers from all over the world!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-title">Why AirTalk?</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          AirTalk has several unique features that make it stand out from other services
        </p>

        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon-large">üí°</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Out Of The Box</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Everything you need to voice call with others is built in the website without the need to download any 
              additional softwares. You can use it on any device (desktop computer, tablet, mobile) and any OS 
              (Windows/Mac, iOS/Android).
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon-large">üé§</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Voice Only</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Don't want to be on camera? Don't worry, we've got you covered. AirTalk is based on the idea where 
              people don't want to be on camera but want to speak with someone. This way, it helps you interact with 
              others on an equal footing without any camera-related expectations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon-large">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Safe & Peer-To-Peer</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              When we say peer to peer conversations we really mean it. There is no server in between two partners. 
              The data is going through directly between two partners. This means there is no way to listen in to anyones 
              private conversation. To provide full blown safety, all connections are end-to-end encrypted.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon-large">‚ôø</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Accessibility</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              It was made with a minimalistic, simple user interface. The interface was developed with the users in mind 
              and we paid extra care to make it friendly for people who are visually impaired.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon-large">üöÄ</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">Easy Start</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Getting started is easy, quick and doesn't even require you to sign up. It's convenient and doesn't require 
              personal information. It allows you to get in and start talking right away.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reasons-section">
          <h2 class="section-title">Why People Use AirTalk</h2>
          
          <ul class="reasons-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Anonymous conversations to escape:</strong> People seek anonymous conversations to escape their otherwise 
              mundane lives. The anonymity enables you to express your true self by keeping your identity a secret until you 
              reveal yourself to the person you're speaking to. You don't have to submit a photo or share your original name; 
              you are free to use creative nicknames for yourself.
            </li>
            
            <li>
              <strong>Improve your social skills:</strong> Social skills are so necessary, especially in today's world for both 
              your personal and professional success. Many successful people would tell you that good social skills are key to 
              success. Like any other skill, your social skills will improve the more you use them and decrease when you don't, 
              just like any other skill. Daily interactions with strangers give you an ideal opportunity to hone and develop your 
              skills. The more you interact with people you have never spoken to, the more you learn how to strike up a conversation, 
              engage in meaningful dialogue with people and end a conversation.
            </li>
            
            <li>
              <strong>Practice and improve your language:</strong> Many people already have decent communication abilities but 
              merely feel bored and want to talk with someone. However, some people want to improve their communication and English 
              speaking abilities while chatting with strangers. AirTalk is a great place to enhance language and communication skills, 
              especially if you live in a city that has a large number of non-English speaking people.
            </li>
            
            <li>
              <strong>Build genuine connections:</strong> Building genuine and long-lasting connections with others who share your 
              values and interests is possible with the help of this modest yet effective system. It is a great way to expand your 
              network beyond the physical location. You can ask questions, get responses, offer guidance or advice, assist others, 
              and make new friends. When you're bored or lonely, call someone and socialise.
            </li>
            
            <li>
              <strong>Express your talents:</strong> This platform makes it simple to pursue your ambitions, regardless of whether 
              you're a writer concerned about how comments or reviews will be posted online or if you have a knack for singing or 
              poetry but are too shy, reluctant, or fearful to share it with your peers. No matter how weird you may think they are, 
              rest assured that there are others out there who share your goals and aspirations.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-dark) 0%, var(--bg-darker) 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-light) 0%, var(--accent-light) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .about-content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--bg-darker);
  }

  .about-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-illustration {
    font-size: 8rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .feature-icon-large {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .reasons-section {
    margin-top: 5rem;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .reasons-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .reasons-list li {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .reasons-list li::before {
    content: "‚Üí";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary-light);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .reasons-list strong {
    color: var(--text);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-intro {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-illustration {
      font-size: 5rem;
    }

    .reasons-list li {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>

